            "text_ABA4N8": {
              "type": "text",
              "name": "t:names.text",
              "settings": {
                "custom_css": "",
                "text": "<p>The launch of Dance Moms transformed ALDC from a respected competitive studio into a global cultural phenomenon.<br/><br/>The series offered an unfiltered look into the realities of competitive dance training — showcasing ambition, pressure, dedication, and the pursuit of perfection. It sparked worldwide conversations about dance education and brought unprecedented attention to the competitive dance industry.<br/><br/>Through television, interviews, guest appearances, and digital media, Abby Lee Miller became one of the most recognizable figures in dance</p>",
