              "name": "t:names.text",
              "settings": {
                "custom_css": "",
                "text": "<p>Known for her tough-love approach and eye for talent, Abby shares exclusive behind-the-scenes content, dance tutorials, reaction videos, and her candid take on all things dance and entertainment. Viewers can expect personal stories, never-before-seen footage from her time on Dance Moms, and insights into the dance industry straight from the source. Whether you're a longtime fan or new to the world of competitive dance, Abby’s channel is a front-row seat to the drama, the discipline, and the drive that made her a household name.</p>",
